name: Schöne und gut gelegene Wohnung
description: Quiet apartment, 15 min. by public transport to the main train station. Ideal for exploring the city. One bedroom with double bed (2 mattresses), a large living/dining area with 2 sofa beds (these with very good mattresses!).
neighborhood_overview: Ideal for exploring the central in-circle 3,4 and 5 on foot. The train station is 5 minutes from the apartment and the main train station is a 15-minute walk away. Nice cafe ("Salut Salon") next to the apartment (best coffee in town).

name: Modern 1 room apartment in district 4
description:
The newly renovated and luxuriously furnished apartment is just a 10-15 minute walk from the main train station, Paradeplatz or Europaallee, amidst many restaurants and bars.

A kitchen with a stovetop; refrigerator and microwave, a shower in the private bathroom inviting you to relax, a digital TV/photo frame (for your own photos or as a painting on the wall) and a fiber-optic Internet connection are just some of the highlights of this great one-bedroom apartment.

name: Cozy studio in Niederdof
description:
Welcome to your cozy studio in the heart of Zurich! This charming and inviting space is the perfect home base for your travels to this beautiful city.

Located in a prime location, our studio is just steps away from all of the best that Zurich has to offer. Whether you want to explore the historic old town, wander through the trendy shops and cafes of the Bahnhofstrasse, or take in the breathtaking views of Lake Zurich, everything is right at your doorstep.

name: 2.5 room furnished apartment
description:
Enjoy a stylish experience at this centrally-located place.

This is the place I live and put it on Airbnb when I go in vacation. So it may not be a tipical AirBnB but it will be how locals live here :).

bus 72 is right next to the house. many public transport (tram 13, 5 and 3 train stations) within 5 minutes walk.

lake is 10min walk.

supermarket/mall is 5 minutes walk.

name: Renggerstrasse Room 2 Interim Homes Zurich
description:
Large business room (20m2) with your own balcony in the heart of Zurich.

The flat hosts 4 people and you share kitchen, bathroom, WC and hallway.

Shared areas are cleaned by our staff every two weeks.

Everything you need for your stay is available in the room.

Everything included.
You can register your new address with the authorities.

Great location:
- 5 minutes walking distance to the Zurich lake or the train station Wollishofen
- 13 minutes to Zurich main station with public transport
